author: codex-duplication-audit
acceptance_criteria: "Beads and Todos packages share common adapter/runtime helpers for repeated command metadata, source mapping, import counters, and result rendering; package-specific field mapping remains explicit; beads/todos unit tests and package smoke coverage pass; pnpm build passes."
